# This file keeps the assets directory in git.
#
# SAM3 ONNX Assets for Browser-Side Inference
# ============================================
#
# DECODER (for interactive annotation):
# - tracker_decoder.onnx (22MB) - HuggingFace unified decoder with mask refinement
# - tracker-prompt-encoder-mask-decoder-with-mask-input.onnx (17MB) - alternate
#
# NOTE: Memory components (memory_attention, memory_encoder, object_pointer)
# run SERVER-SIDE only. Video propagation uses CVAT tracker interface with
# Redis-backed state management. Do not add memory models to browser assets.
#
# To generate decoder, run the export script in serverless/pytorch/facebookresearch/sam3/nuclio/:
#
#   python export_hf_onnx.py
#
# All exports use opset 17 for onnxruntime-web 1.14.0 compatibility.
